&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a dynamic Regional Sales Manager to take ownership of a defined territory across the UK, driving growth with machine builders and manufacturing end users. This hands-on commercial role demands a blend of technical engineering knowledge and solution-based selling to develop new business and strengthen customer relationships.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive sales growth across the defined territory, targeting both machine builders and manufacturing end users.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage technical engineering knowledge to provide solution-based selling strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain strong customer relationships, ensuring long-term partnerships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a liaison between customers and engineering teams to ensure clear communication of technical requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and pursue new business opportunities within the manufacturing engineering environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a thorough understanding of how equipment, components, and systems fit into wider production processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver effective sales presentations and negotiations to close deals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in technical sales within a manufacturing or engineering environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong engineering or technical understanding, with the ability to interpret drawings or specifications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience selling to machine builders and manufacturing businesses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to translate technical requirements into practical, commercially viable solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent relationship-building skills with both technical and commercial stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-motivated with strong organizational skills and the ability to manage a territory independently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confident communicator with strong negotiation skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commercially aware, with a focus on delivering results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
